  "detailed_description": "Calling all heroes! Prepare yourself for an epic battle in this captivating tower defense game! Build, defend, and triumph as you strategically place towers, manage resources, and upgrade your arsenal to fend off relentless waves of enemies.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/fa4caf0d5eb013f2de3fcd8db8129ee6.poster.avif?t=1719331288\" width=480 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/fa4caf0d5eb013f2de3fcd8db8129ee6.webm?t=1719331288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/fa4caf0d5eb013f2de3fcd8db8129ee6.mp4?t=1719331288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>New!!! Endless Mode. The original mode is now called Survival Mode.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>With distinctive upgrades in your hands, choose your own path to defeat the enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Unique playthrough. No two games are the same!</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>NG+ new game mode. Higher difficulty with stronger enemies.</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Score ranking. Challenge yourself to be the best. Speedrun anyone?</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/637083a368f6799b56a6fabcdb9fbfec.poster.avif?t=1719331288\" width=480 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/637083a368f6799b56a6fabcdb9fbfec.webm?t=1719331288\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2728240/extras/637083a368f6799b56a6fabcdb9fbfec.mp4?t=1719331288\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
